FBIS4-20950 "jptdd014__l94010" JPRS-TDD-94-014-L JPRS Narcotics 25 March 1994 LATIN AMERICA BOLIVIA Court Orders Opening of Proceedings Against MIR Leaders Court Orders Opening of Proceedings Against MIR Leaders PY2503215794 La Paz Television Nacional Network in Spanish 1700 GMT 25 Mar 94 PY2503215794 La Paz Television Nacional Network Spanish BFN [Text] Fides News Agency reports that the La Paz 1st Controlled Substances Court [Juzgado Primero de Substancias Controladas] has ordered the opening of judiciary police proceedings against Oscar Eid Franco, Susana Seleme, and other aides of former President Jaime Paz Zamora, and has ruled that former Interior Minister Guillermo Capobianco and former Santa Cruz Mayor Rolando Arostegui may be tried by a court for their alleged involvement with drug trafficker Isaac "Oso" Chavarria.
